			[2026] paragraph ''
				StaticText "One downside to manual jar downloads is that you don't keep up-to-date with the latest released version. We have a Bash launcher script at"
				[2027] link 'bin/utils/openapi-generator.cli.sh', url='http://127.0.0.1:8023/OpenAPITools/openapi-generator/-/blob/master/bin/utils/openapi-generator-cli.sh'

				StaticText ''
				StaticText 'chmod u+x ~/bin/openapitools/openapi-generator-cli'
				StaticText ''
				StaticText 'export PATH=$PATH:~/bin/openapitools/'
